config MHI_BUS_PCI_GENERIC
	tristate "MHI PCI controller driver"
	depends on MHI_BUS
	depends on PCI
	help
	  This driver provides MHI PCI controller driver for devices such as
	  Qualcomm SDX55 based PCIe modems.

